						               													<description>Don't Get Mad is an exciting, fast moving game where all players must stake points from the cards in their 'hand' on the outcome of general knowledge questions - or - on a unique variety of dice rolls. There are over 1,000 great questions from 70 wide ranging categories where most questions offer multiple choices. But before a player stakes any points, all they will know on any question, is its subject and how many possible choices there are! The most unusual (mischievous) quirk allows players to choose whether they wish to Play or to Pass (to an opponent) or to make challenges. Whatever the 'in-player' decides to do, they will always decide on the number of points that are to be staked. Unlike; with most other board game 'classics'; no player can ever go 'OUT' of the game until the game is fully over!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players: 2-6 or teams.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
